graph TB
    User[👤 User Layer]
    
    CLI["📟 CLI Interface"]
    Web["🌐 Streamlit Web App"]
    
    User -->|Input Query| CLI
    User -->|Input Query| Web
    
    subgraph AppLayer["🔧 Application Layer"]
        Config["Config Manager<br/>python-dotenv"]
        Agent["LangChain SQL Agent<br/>Query Orchestrator"]
        Export["Export Module<br/>CSV Export"]
        Viz["Visualization Module<br/>matplotlib/plotly"]
    end
    
    CLI -->|Execute| Agent
    Web -->|Execute| Agent
    
    Agent -->|Read Config| Config
    Agent -->|Export Data| Export
    Agent -->|Visualize| Viz
    
    subgraph AzureLayer["☁️ Azure Services Layer"]
        LLM["Azure OpenAI<br/>LLM API"]
        Auth["Azure Identity<br/>Token Service"]
        EntraID["Microsoft Entra ID<br/>Identity Provider"]
    end
    
    Agent -->|LLM Request| LLM
    Agent -->|Get Token| Auth
    Auth -->|Authenticate| EntraID
    
    subgraph DataLayer["💾 Data Layer"]
        SQLAlchemy["SQLAlchemy<br/>ORM Engine"]
        PyODBC["pyodbc<br/>Driver"]
        FabricDB["Microsoft Fabric SQL<br/>Data Warehouse"]
    end
    
    Agent -->|Generate SQL| SQLAlchemy
    SQLAlchemy -->|Execute Query| PyODBC
    PyODBC -->|Connect & Query| FabricDB
    
    FabricDB -->|Results| PyODBC
    PyODBC -->|Data| SQLAlchemy
    SQLAlchemy -->|Rows| Agent
    
    LLM -->|Response| Agent
    Auth -->|Token| PyODBC
    
    Agent -->|Results| Export
    Agent -->|Results| Viz
    Export -->|CSV File| User
    Viz -->|Chart| User
    
    style User fill:#e1f5ff
    style AppLayer fill:#fff3e0
    style AzureLayer fill:#f3e5f5
    style DataLayer fill:#e8f5e9
    style Agent fill:#ffe0b2
    style LLM fill:#e1bee7
    style FabricDB fill:#c8e6c9